feat: React 18 upgrade, test suite, mobile responsive polish

React 18 Upgrade:
- Upgraded react and react-dom from 17.0.1 to 18
- Migrated from ReactDOM.render to createRoot API
- Build and all features verified working

Test Suite (39 tests, 4 suites):
- snippets.test.js: CRUD, defaults, corruption handling (8 tests)
- gistSync.test.js: token management, sync state, mergeNotes (11 tests)
