- useMarkDown.test.js: rendering, code blocks, footnotes, wiki links, Zendesk (12 tests)
- Added setupTests.js with @testing-library/jest-dom
- Fixed snippet ID collision (added random suffix)

Mobile Responsive Polish:
- Settings panel: scrollable tabs, stacked action cards, responsive danger zone
- Version history: stacked layout (list on top, preview below) on mobile
- Slash menu: width-constrained to viewport
- View toolbar: wraps on narrow screens
- Touch targets: min 36px buttons, tap-highlight disabled
- Editor toolbar: horizontal scroll on overflow
- Tags: proper wrapping on small screens
- Variable prompt and language picker: viewport-constrained
- Table converter: responsive padding
- Extra-small (400px): further compression of tabs, buttons, dividers

New devDeps: @testing-library/react, @testing-library/jest-dom, @testing-library/user-event
New files: src/setupTests.js, src/__tests__/*.test.js
